# CIOS Full Project Setup

## Backend Setup

```powershell
cd backend

py -3.11 -m venv venv

.\venv\Scripts\Activate

python -m pip install --upgrade pip

pip install -r requirements.txt

copy .env.example .env

set DATABASE_URL=sqlite+aiosqlite:///./cios_dev.db

python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000

Backend API Docs:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

Now in a split terminal run the following:

## Frontend Setup

```powershell
cd frontend

npm install

npm start

If npm start does not work:

npm run 

Then use:

npm run dev

